results.name: Number of 10's in the last section of the set of partitions of n.
comment: Zero together with the first differences of A024794. Also number of occurrences of 10 in all partitions of n that do not contain 1 as a part. For the definition of "last section of n" see A135010. It appears that the sums of ten successive terms give the partition numbers A000041.
formula: It appears that A000041(n) = Sum_{j=1..10} a(n+j), n >= 0.
program: (Sage) A206560 = lambda n: sum(list(p).count(10) for p in Partitions(n) if 1 not in p)
xref: Column 10 of A182703 and of A194812.
results.author: _Omar E. Pol_, Feb 09 2012
